2.118. PreviousVehicleInfo
Information related to the vehicle previously used by a driver when 
inserting his card in a vehicle unit (Annex 1B requirement 081 and 
Annex 1C requirement 102).
Generation 1:
vehicleRegistrationIdentification is the VRN and the registering 
Member State of the vehicle.
cardWithdrawalTime is the card withdrawal date and time.
Generation 2:
In addition to generation 1 the following data element is used:
vuGeneration identifies the generation of the vehicle unit.
